
** Counter

  - *C-x C-k C-i* Insert a macro counter. Arg specifies the
    increment.

  - *C-u 5 f1* - set the counter to five
  - *f1*       - inserts the actual counter and increments it
  - *C-u 2 f1* - increments it by two 

** Edit

  - *C-x C-k C-e* Edit the macro.

** Name It

  - name-last-kbd-macro
  - insert-kbd-macro

** Ring

  - C-x C-k C-p
  - C-x C-k C-n

** Delete

  - C-x C-k C-d


